00:12:19.040 --> 00:12:22.170 align:middle line:84%
I find this to be true
that I can break off

00:12:22.170 --> 00:12:25.550 align:middle line:84%
the square of a high
quality chocolate bar,

00:12:25.550 --> 00:12:27.150 align:middle line:84%
let it slowly
dissolve in my mouth

00:12:27.150 --> 00:12:28.400 align:middle line:90%
