00:12:28.400 --> 00:12:33.350 align:middle line:84%
But you obviously have
a very fine character.

00:12:33.350 --> 00:12:35.150 align:middle line:84%
>> I think it's
possible to do that.

00:12:35.150 --> 00:12:37.145 align:middle line:84%
Similarly, if you're
out in a restaurant,

00:12:37.145 --> 00:12:40.310 align:middle line:84%
and you want a dessert, so
order a dessert for the table,

00:12:40.310 --> 00:12:42.500 align:middle line:84%
and have a bite of
it or a bite or two.

00:12:42.500 --> 00:12:43.605 align:middle line:90%
