00:12:47.780 --> 00:12:49.100 align:middle line:90%
or craving it.

00:12:49.100 --> 00:12:50.870 align:middle line:84%
But actually, I really
am more concerned

00:12:50.870 --> 00:12:52.250 align:middle line:84%
about a lot of
the starchy things

00:12:52.250 --> 00:12:54.410 align:middle line:90%
we eat than the sugary things.

00:12:54.410 --> 00:12:57.710 align:middle line:84%
And a very simple tip
for people in restaurants

00:12:57.710 --> 00:13:01.820 align:middle line:84%
is to tell waiters not to bring
bread and butter until the meal

00:13:01.820 --> 00:13:03.980 align:middle line:90%
