00:13:03.980 --> 00:13:07.490 align:middle line:84%
It is so easy to load up on
a vast amount of calories

00:13:07.490 --> 00:13:11.780 align:middle line:84%
of the worst kind of
starch even before you

00:13:11.780 --> 00:13:14.370 align:middle line:90%
get to eating your appetizer.

00:13:14.370 --> 00:13:17.340 align:middle line:84%
>> So what would be a
diet that would be--

00:13:17.340 --> 00:13:19.920 align:middle line:84%
let's reduce it down to
just a couple of things.

00:13:19.920 --> 00:13:22.860 align:middle line:84%
>> OK, great, well, the diet
that I recommend in this book I

00:13:22.860 --> 00:13:23.892 align:middle line:90%
think will help people.

00:13:23.892 --> 00:13:26.100 align:middle line:84%
First of all, I'd like to
shift the conversation some

00:13:26.100 --> 00:13:28.415 align:middle line:84%
